{"tid":2419623,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK 抵達韓團新境界　〈DDU-DU DDU-DU〉MV 破 15 億！","createTime":"2021-02-23T11:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T07:03:23.000Z","uid":16659,"like":12,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7a40edbec805aa569d4badcc9d8d2f5e3d886647","tid":2419623,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_fea5f43aa4373f9a8d8c2b7c71038581/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-23/133860-897853.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_fea5f43aa4373f9a8d8c2b7c71038581%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-23%2F133860-897853.png&h=163a118a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKPINK 的 &ldquo;DDU-DU DDU-DU&rdquo; 發行未滿三年，觀看次數又再度寫下了新紀錄！<br />\n<br />\n在今天（23 日）韓國時間傍晚 5 點半左右，BLACKPINK 的 &ldquo;DDU-DU DDU-DU&rdquo; 官方 MV 觀看次數跨越了驚人的 15 億大關，成為史上第一支獲得這個成績的韓國團體 MV。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_98db0ff094053dba85c15ac81c1fc07f/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-23/133860-897852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_98db0ff094053dba85c15ac81c1fc07f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-23%2F133860-897852.jpg&h=52697ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;DDU-DU DDU-DU&rdquo; 於 2018 年 6 月 15 日發行，是 BLACKPINK 在出道近兩年後才首度推出的迷你專輯主打歌。挟著粉絲的高度期待，這首歌一發行就勢如破竹，接連創造各種「最快」、「最高」的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IHNzOHi8sJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIHNzOHi8sJs&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv3xV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=0e070d51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IHNzOHi8sJs</a><br />\n<br />\n去年 11 月，BLACKPINK 憑著 &ldquo;DDU-DU DDU-DU&rdquo; 成為史上第一組擁有 10 億 MV 的韓國團體，其後 MV 觀看次數仍穩定上升，每隔 2~4 個月又會多出一億，儘管發行許久依然享有高人氣！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：YG Entertainment）"},{"pid":"d834c95866c04d60a7313f38cc1272aa938a20c4","tid":2419623,"u